urls.title: BT announces regional rollout schedule for Digital Voice

1706566776480260115.text:
The landline is here to stay, but the technology used to make calls is changing from analogue to digital. Today we announce the next phase in our rollout of this service coming to our customers across the UK on a region-by-region basis. #DigitalSwitchover
